@startuml
title UC-OPS-001 Data Flow

actor User
participant Form1
participant TrafficSvc
participant CctvSvc

User -> Form1 : 연속 조회 클릭
Form1 -> Form1 : Interlocked.Increment(requestVersion)
Form1 -> TrafficSvc : 트래픽 조회(또는)
Form1 -> CctvSvc : CCTV 조회
TrafficSvc --> Form1 : 결과
Form1 -> Form1 : requestVersion 비교 후 최신만 반영
@enduml
